name: 2023 10th International Conference on Bioinformatics Research and Applications
content: Paper Publication: Previously, the papers of ICBRA have been published in International Conference Proceedings by ACM, indexed by Ei Compendex and Scopus since 2017\. Accepted and registered papers of ICBRA 2023 will be published in International Conference Proceedings, which will be indexed by Ei Compendex and Scopus, and submitted to be reviewed by CPCI.
